<div id="root-intro">
  <div class="intro-content valign-wrapper">
    <div class="container valign">
        <center>
          <div class="intro-text">
            <div class="intro-padding hide-on-med-and-up"></div>
            <h1><span class="hide-on-small-only">Welcome to Tower Automotive</h1></span>
            <h2><span class="hide-on-med-and-up">Tower Automotive</h2></span>
            <h4>What Drives You?<br></h4>
          </div>
          <div class="row hide-on-small-only">
            <div class="big-search-button">
              <div class="col s12">
                <a href="<%= inventory_url %>">
                  <div class="card white big-search-btn valign-wrapper hoverable">
                    <div class="card-content blue-grey-text text-darken-1 valign">
                      <span class="card-title">
                        <button class="btn-floating waves-effect waves-teal"><i class="material-icons">search</i></button> Inventory Search
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>         
            <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
              <a class='waves-effect waves-light btn-large intro-btn right dropdown-button' data-hover="true" href='#' data-activates='service-drop-hm'>Service</a>
              <ul id='service-drop-hm' class='dropdown-content'>
                  <li><a href="<%= service_url %>">Service</a></li>
                  <li><a href="<%= parts_url %>">Parts</a></li>
                  <li><a href="<%= bodyshop_url %>">Bodyshop</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
              <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large intro-btn" href="<%= finance_url %>">Finance</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12 m4 l4">
              <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large intro-btn left modal-trigger" href="#login-modal">Log In</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row hide-on-med-and-up">
            <div class="big-search-button">
              <div class="col s12">
                <a href="<%= inventory_url %>">
                  <div class="card white big-search-btn valign-wrapper hoverable">
                    <div class="card-content blue-grey-text text-darken-1 valign">
                      <span class="card-title">
                        <button class="btn-floating waves-effect waves-teal"><i class="material-icons">search</i></button> Inventory Search
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>                   
            <div class="col s12">
              <a class='waves-effect waves-light btn-large intro-btn full-width dropdown-button' href='#' data-activates='service-drop-hm-mob'>Service</a>
              <ul id='service-drop-hm-mob' class='dropdown-content'>
                  <li><a href="<%= service_url %>">Service</a></li>
                  <li><a href="<%= parts_url %>">Parts</a></li>
                  <li><a href="<%= bodyshop_url %>">Bodyshop</a></li>
              </ul>              
            </div>
            <div class="col s12">
              <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large intro-btn full-width" href="<%= finance_url %>">Finance</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col s12">
              <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large intro-btn full-width login-modal" href="#login-modal">Log In</a>
            </div>
          </div>          
        </center>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="intro-search valign-wrapper">
    <div class="container valign">
      <div class="card-panel hoverable intro-search-card">  
        <table class="intro-search-table">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="intro-search-cell-1">
                <div class="input-field col s12">
                  <select>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>What's Your Favorite Color?</option>
                    <option value="1">Red</option>
                    <option value="2">Black</option>
                    <option value="3">Blue</option>
                  </select>
                  <label class="teal-text" style="margin-left: -10px;">Color</label>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="intro-search-cell-2">
                <div class="input-field col s12">
                  <select>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Find Your Brand.</option>
                    <option value="1">Ford</option>
                    <option value="2">Chevrolet</option>
                    <option value="3">Dodge</option>
                  </select>
                  <label class="teal-text" style="margin-left: -10px;">Make</label>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="intro-search-cell-3">
                <div class="input-field col s12">
                  <select>
                    <option value="" disabled selected>What's Your Style?</option>
                    <option value="1">Car</option>
                    <option value="2">Truck</option>
                    <option value="3">SUV</option>
                    <option value="4">Mini-Van</option>
                  </select>
                  <label class="teal-text" style="margin-left: -10px;">Body</label>
                </div>
              </td>                                 
              <td class="intro-search-cell-4">
                <a href="<%= inventory_url %>"><button class="intro-search-btn btn-large btn-floating waves-effect waves-teal"><i class="material-icons" href="<%= inventory_url %>">search</i></button></a>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>                                  
    </div>
  </div>
</div>  

  <div class="section">
    <div class="container"><br>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col l4 m10 push-m1">
          <div class="card blue-grey darken-1">
            <div class="card-content white-text">
              <span class="card-title"><blockquote>What's It Worth?</blockquote></span>
              <p>Knowledge is power. Car buying power. Find out what your car is worth right now and let it's value work for <em>you</em>.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action right-align">
              <a href="<%= value_url %>">Discover</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col l4 m10 push-m1">
          <div class="card blue-grey darken-1">
            <div class="card-content white-text">
              <span class="card-title"><blockquote>Sell Us Your Car</blockquote></span>
              <p>We need more cars! With so many happy customers, it's hard to keep up with demand. Sell us your car today and bring home some extra cash</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action right-align">
              <a href="<%= sellcar_url %>">Let's Go</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col l4 m10 push-m1">
          <div class="card blue-grey darken-1">
            <div class="card-content white-text">
              <span class="card-title"><blockquote>Trade Up</blockquote></span>
              <p>Let your car work for you. <em>No one</em> gives you more for your trade than Tower. Let us show you how far your trade can go!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-action right-align">
              <a href="<%= trade_url %>">Get Started</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
